usion of the charged $D\\bar{D}^*$ channel) turn\nout to have a moderate impact on the results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2011 16:40:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2011 12:47:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
