ructure of this model (in particular, the\nappeal to gambler's ruin) will be similar to GRW collapse models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2011 22:20:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2011 19:57:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 Mar 2012 17:34:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-14"}
