d cannot be eliminated if we want to perform fault-tolerant classical\ncomputing.\n  Keywords: Nanomagnetic logic, multiferroics, straintronics and spintronics,\nLandau-Lifshitz-Gilbert equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2011 21:23:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-14"}
