, underscoring the need to distinguish\nbetween the personal and the public perspectives of introductory modern physics\nstudents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2011 02:26:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
